narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes it'd be good to come into the class with a good idea of what you want out of it, in terms of project ideas/technical skills/feedback.

Art 401 is for those interested in photography as an art form. It is a serious class with a higher level of discourse. Taking Art 401 broadened my understanding of contemporary photography and just what it means to produce a photograph that might be considered art. Prepare to work hard and make images you might never have been able to conceive yourself.
